Bonnie-Jill Laflin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bonnie-Jill_Laflin 0 Bonnie-Jill Laflin (born March 15, 1976) is an American model, television personality and sportscaster. Laflin has also worked as an actress and most notably as a scout for the Los Angeles Lakers, making her the league's first female scout. She was also assistant general manager of the Lakers NBA Development League team. Bonnie-Jill_Laflin ( born March_15_,_1976 ) is an_American_model , television_personality_and_sportscaster .
